        <mxCell id="gb8ywaOI7upkZd4ps1_8-18" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;div align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;Notes:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;- Ideally we&#39;ll use an orchestration framework (e.g. Airflow, Prefect) instead of an HTTP webapp like FastAPI.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;- Orchestration will have built-in features as follows:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- Scheduling&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- Manual Trigger is also supported&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- Retries&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- State handling&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- Caching (for idempotent resources)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- Monitoring&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
